                                 Encapsulation:
                                                                               <<20-02-26>>
-> Encapsulation is a most powerfull conceptof oop concept which bind different diffreent 
data member and member function in single entity and provide data hiding for outside the 
world.


-> encapsulation concept is achieve by class and object examle.

1> data hiding
2> data prevent from outside world
3> security no one can directly change from outside the world
4> data control no one can add unwanted value or apply changes